metadata.name: Trypophobia
metadata.description:
This art is my attempt to overcome myself.  This is my fear, my disease.  Even from an accidental glance, I feel sick, my body is thrown into heat and trembling, and my mind is seized by panic.  Everyone has their own phobia, and the best way to deal with it is to face it face to face.  Fight!
1/1 digital art  3508*2480  300 dpi
